name: Fiat 128
description:
Get ready for some action with new unleaded plasma engines, remanufactured gravitators, and interior tuning including new stereo with Bluetooth and Spotify. The best companion for the youth eager to paint the town red.

Digital illustration, 300 dpi, 4245 x 5118  pixels

Collection: Universo Chatarra Deluxe Edition
A special collection of vintage cars from around the world, as depicted in the Universo Chatarra (Junkyard Universe) series: old-fashioned, dystopic, and strangely glamorous floating machines.

By Alejandro Burdisio (Burda), February 17th, 2022.
